{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "internal": "labs::inside_face_uvs::1.0", "icon": "SOP/uvunwrap", "tags": "sidefxlabs, break, gamedev", "version": "1.0", "namespace": "labs"}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Labs Inside Face UVs"], "extent": [0, 25]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": [" Create UV\u2019s for inside faces of Voronoi fractured geometry. "], "extent": [145, 214]}, {"type": "video_group", "body": [{"ext": null, "type": "video", "indent": 0, "role": "item", "extent": [214, 222], "body": [], "container": true, "attrs": {"src": "/movies/insideuvs.mp4"}}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["Voronoi fracture can generate interior faces, but won\u2019t create UV\u2019s. The Inside Face UVs HDA will generate automatic UV\u2019s for these interior faces."], "extent": [254, 403]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["The only requirement is that 'inside' and 'outside' groups have been defined by the Voronoi fracture sop, which is the default behavior."], "extent": [403, 541]}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [541, 553], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Group"], "extent": [553, 564], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["A subset of primitives to apply the operation to."], "extent": [564, 622]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 4, "text": ["UV"], "extent": [622, 635], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Inside Group"], "extent": [635, 653], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The group the operation should be applied to."], "extent": [653, 707]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Attribute"], "extent": [707, 722], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The attribute name to be used for generating UVs for."], "extent": [722, 784]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Tiling"], "extent": [784, 796], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Amount of UV space to use; 1 will use the 0-1 range, 2 will use 0-2 etc."], "extent": [796, 877]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Flattening Method"], "extent": [877, 900], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["How to flatten 3d geometry into UV space, see the 'UV flatten' sop help for details."], "extent": [900, 994]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 4, "text": ["Normals"], "extent": [994, 1012], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Compute Normals"], "extent": [1012, 1033], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["Toggle if new normals should be generated for the specified inside group."], "extent": [1033, 1115]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Cusp Angle"], "extent": [1115, 1131], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The cusp angle to be used when generating normals."], "extent": [1131, 1190]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 4, "text": ["Weighting Method"], "extent": [1190, 1212], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 8, "text": ["The weighting method to be used when generating normals."], "extent": [1212, 1282]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}], "text": "Parameters"}], "title": ["Labs Inside Face UVs"], "summary": [" Create UV\u2019s for inside faces of Voronoi fractured geometry. "]}